### Serve index.html
GET http://127.0.0.1:7878/
Accept: text/html

###

### 404 Not Found (non-existent file)
GET http://127.0.0.1:7878/error
Accept: text/html

###

### Slow response (sleep 5s)
GET http://127.0.0.1:7878/sleep
Accept: text/html

###

### Simple JSON API
GET http://127.0.0.1:7878/api/hello
Accept: application/json

###

### List all users (initially empty)
GET http://127.0.0.1:7878/users
Accept: application/json

###

### List users filtered by name or age
# by name contains "li"
GET http://127.0.0.1:7878/users?name=li
Accept: application/json

# by exact age
GET http://127.0.0.1:7878/users?age=30
Accept: application/json

# both filters
GET http://127.0.0.1:7878/users?name=li&age=30
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new user
POST http://127.0.0.1:7878/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice",
  "age": 30
}

