### Math operations
#### Addition
POST http://127.0.0.1:7878/math
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operator": "+",
  "arg1": 10,
  "arg2": 5
}

#### Subtraction
POST http://127.0.0.1:7878/math
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operator": "-",
  "arg1": 10,
  "arg2": 5
}

#### Multiplication
POST http://127.0.0.1:7878/math
Content-Type: application/json

